Vaccines Are Coming. But First, a Long, Dark Winter.With vaccines and a new administration in the U.S., the pandemic will be tamed. But experts say the coming months “are going to be just horrible.”The nation now must endure a critical period of transition, as it sets aside justifiable optimism about next spring and confronts the dark winter ahead.
